headline: Invictus Foundation™ Receives Grant from CSX to Install a Behavioral Telehealth Platform in its Southeastern Regional Welcome Home Network and Continue the Capital Construction Planning for Eight Regional TBI & Behavioral Health Centers Across the Nation
summary: To the Invictus Foundation, CSX's support represents the best of good corporate citizenship," states Peter J Whalen, Founder and CEO of the Invictus Foundation. "It's tremendously uplifting for the people we represent to see their service validated by a marquee corporate brand such as CSX.
